nodes.text: A fleet of the Corporate Alliance was a naval formation that blockaded the planet Malastare during the Battle of Malastare Narrows over a decade before the Clone Wars.

The fleet was led by Admiral Trench, and using his tactics, it tore into the Republic fleet sent to engage the blockade. The Republic ships barely escaped the battle, and were later reinforced with a Jedi-led task force that destroyed Trench's flagship.
